{"id":6285,"date":"2025-11-18T14:00:27","date_gmt":"2025-11-18T07:00:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=6285"},"modified":"2025-12-27T10:35:30","modified_gmt":"2025-12-27T03:35:30","slug":"tinh-chat-trang-sang-mo-nam-the-he-moi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/tinh-chat-trang-sang-mo-nam-the-he-moi\/","title":{"rendered":"Tinh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng m\u1edd n\u00e1m th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi l\u00e0n da \u00c1 \u0110\u00f4ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u201cTr\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u1ecfe\u201d, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c h\u01a1n v\u1edbi kem tr\u1ed9n, treatment n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4, hay c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, b\u00e0o m\u00f2n da. Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng\u00a0 c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1<\/span>ch h\u00e0ng, D\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m GSC \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 cho ra m\u1eaft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tinh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng &#8211; GSC GIGA WHITE SERUM an to\u00e0n, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh gi\u00fap mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng h\u1ed3ng r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6299\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6299\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/tinh-chat-trang-sang-mo-nam-the-he-moi\/\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6299 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-1.webp\" alt=\"Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng 2026 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6299\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng 2026 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"xu-huong-va-thuc-trang-thi-truong-my-pham-duong-trang-da\"><\/span><b>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t treatment, b\u00f4i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m \u2013 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u2013 tr\u1ecb th\u00e2m, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da y\u1ebfu, d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, bong tr\u00f3c, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nhu c\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd gi\u1ea3m, ch\u1ec9 chuy\u1ec3n d\u1ecbch t\u1eeb \u201cTr\u1eafng c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t\u201d sang \u201cTr\u1eafng kh\u1ecfe t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c\u201d. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ch\u0103m da c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m uy t\u00edn:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a corticoid, ch\u1ea5t l\u1ed9t t\u1ea9y kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hydroquinone kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0o m\u00f2n da hay kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da sau treatment kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 uy t\u00edn kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf melanin kh\u00e1c nhau (Niacinamide, Tranexamic Acid, Arbutin, Glutathione\u2026) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung m\u1ea1nh nh\u00f3m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u2013 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u2013 ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Minh b\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9, xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9, c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tinh-chat-trang-sang-gsc-giga-white\"><\/span><b>Tinh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng GSC Giga White<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Giga White Serum \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Y t\u1ebf Vi\u1ec7t Nam, n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng \u0111i theo c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cao, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n da ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-uu-diem-cong-thuc-cua-gsc-giga-white-serum\"><\/span><b>Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n &amp; \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a GSC Giga White Serum<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00ean s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c Giga White Serum k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p 3 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, m\u1ed7i ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong \u201cchu\u1ed7i\u201d h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh s\u1eafc t\u1ed1:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Niacinamide 5%<\/b><br \/>\n<h5><span style=\"font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px\">Gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n melanin t\u1eeb t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 l\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da y\u1ebfu \u2013 d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng khi d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/h5>\n<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Tranexamic Acid 2%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzym plasmin, gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t melanin. Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn trong h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 n\u00e1m do vi\u00eam v\u00e0 do n\u1eafng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Alpha Arbutin 2%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> D\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng an to\u00e0n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf tyrosinase \u2013 enzym quan tr\u1ecdng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t melanin. Arbutin gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n c\u00e1c m\u1ea3ng t\u1ed1i, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi da t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Serum Giga White h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3: gi\u1ea3m t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t, \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzym t\u1ea1o s\u1eafc t\u1ed1, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n melanin v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi n\u1ec1n da s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi duy tr\u00ec da \u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t n\u00e1m sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ec sao s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh?<\/b><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6295\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6295\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/tinh-chat-trang-sang-mo-nam-the-he-moi\/\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6295 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-2.webp\" alt=\"Tinh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng GSC s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i gi\u00fap hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6295\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng GSC s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i gi\u00fap hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a GSC Giga White Serum \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa n\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>\u201cC\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c v\u00e0ng\u201d l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng \u0111a t\u1ea7ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ebf v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 cao, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap da ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb t\u1eeb, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf k\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt gi\u00e0u ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t \u0111en, Cam \u2013 Chanh \u2013 M\u00eda, B\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh, D\u00e2u t\u1eb1m tr\u1eafng, Cam th\u1ea3o, Rau m\u00e1\u2026 b\u1ed5 sung vitamin, polyphenol, flavonoid, gi\u00fap nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da, t\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 se l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00f9ng da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u2013 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m song song<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sodium Hyaluronate, Glycerin, Betain, Panthenol, Allantoin, Centella Asiatica Extract\u2026 gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m m\u1ecbn, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nano &#8211; th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh h\u01a1n<\/b><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u theo c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ph\u00e2n t\u1eed nano, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u00e0ng d\u00e0y b\u00ed. Sau khi th\u1ea5m, da v\u1eabn m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn, kh\u00f4ng r\u00edt, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i, d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1edbp kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c trang \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-su-dung-gsc-giga-white\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng GSC Giga White<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6296\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6296\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/tinh-chat-trang-sang-mo-nam-the-he-moi\/\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6296 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-3.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng GSC Giga White Serum\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6296\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng GSC Giga White Serum<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t cho:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, da b\u1ecb s\u1ea1m n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang, da s\u1eabm m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da sau m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ebft th\u00e2m t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng \u2013 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da nh\u01b0ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean an to\u00e0n, c\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u0111i k\u00e8m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng cho:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 lan r\u1ed9ng, da \u0111ang nhi\u1ec5m \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1, r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1eb7ng (\u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, bong tr\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai\/cho con b\u00fa: n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 ho\u1eb7c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-moi-ngay-tai-nha\"><\/span><b>D\u00f9ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Quy tr\u00ecnh g\u1ee3i \u00fd:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da (t\u1ea9y trang n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n + s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da v\u1edbi toner\/essence ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng 0,5 ml GSC Giga White Serum, ch\u1ea5m l\u00ean 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m (tr\u00e1n, hai m\u00e1, m\u0169i, c\u1eb1m), t\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 v\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 serum th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m b\u1eb1ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p lo\u1ea1i da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ban ng\u00e0y b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, thoa \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 d\u1eb7m l\u1ea1i theo khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t: 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y (s\u00e1ng \u2013 t\u1ed1i) n\u1ebfu da kh\u1ecfe; v\u1edbi da t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n khi da \u0111\u00e3 quen.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-trong-lieu-trinh-spaclinic\"><\/span><b>D\u00f9ng trong li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh spa\/clinic<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Giga White Serum c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i spa\/clinic:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc serum sau l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u2013 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da, tr\u01b0\u1edbc massage ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p trong c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng \u2013 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau khi da \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh (kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng ngay tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n da \u0111ang bong tr\u00f3c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi peel, laser, treatment \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh b\u1edfi b\u00e1c s\u0129\/chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u ho\u1eb7c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-bao-quan-gsc-giga-white\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n GSC Giga White<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef da an to\u00e0n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng chung v\u1edbi treatment g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh khi da \u0111ang y\u1ebfu<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng l\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao AHA\/BHA, Retinoid m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n da \u0111ang t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p, n\u00ean c\u00f3 ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>\u01afu ti\u00ean ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng da<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng n\u00e0o ph\u00e1t huy tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n n\u1ebfu da li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u01a1i n\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u201cb\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c\u201d khi d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1edd n\u00e1m \u2013 th\u00e2m \u2013 t\u00e0n nhang.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n n\u01a1i kh\u00f4 m\u00e1t, tr\u00e1nh \u00e1nh n\u1eafng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u1edf n\u01a1i tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, tr\u00e1nh \u1ea9m v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh n\u00f3ng, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 trong xe h\u01a1i ho\u1eb7c n\u01a1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cao k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>\u0110\u00f3ng n\u1eafp k\u1ef9 sau khi d\u00f9ng<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1edf n\u1eafp qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u, v\u1eb7n ch\u1eb7t sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 oxy h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"faq-%e2%80%93-cau-hoi-thuong-gap-ve-gsc-giga-white-serum\"><\/span><b>FAQ \u2013 C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p v\u1ec1 GSC Giga White Serum<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6297\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6297\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/tinh-chat-trang-sang-mo-nam-the-he-moi\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6297 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-4.webp\" alt=\"Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc g\u00ec khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng GSC Giga White Serum\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/80-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6297\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc g\u00ec khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng GSC Giga White Serum<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-giga-white-serum-co-dung-duoc-cho-da-nhay-cam-khong\"><\/span><b style=\"font-size: 16px\">GSC Giga White Serum c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u00f3m l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u2013 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu (Sodium Hyaluronate, Panthenol, Rau m\u00e1, Allantoin\u2026). Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i l\u00e0n da kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, n\u00ean:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Test th\u1eed \u1edf v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ecf (d\u01b0\u1edbi tai\/\u1edf m\u00e1 g\u1ea7n mang tai) trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, theo d\u00f5i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u0103ng t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, n\u00ean ng\u01b0ng v\u00e0 tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-lau-thi-thay-sang-da\"><\/span><b>Bao l\u00e2u th\u00ec th\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng da?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y v\u00e0o:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e1m \u2013 s\u1ea1m \u2013 th\u00e2m ban \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f3i quen ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi routine t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ed1t, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn da s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n sau v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n. N\u00e1m \u2013 s\u1ea1m \u2013 t\u00e0n nhang l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e3n t\u00ednh, c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u201ctr\u1eafng b\u1eadt t\u00f4ng\u201d sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-chung-voi-retinolahabha-duoc-khong\"><\/span><b>D\u00f9ng chung v\u1edbi Retinol\/AHA\/BHA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 treatment ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng l\u00fac nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu da ch\u01b0a quen.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi routine c\u00f3 Retinol\/AHA\/BHA, n\u00ean:<\/span>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng Giga White v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng + m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng acid\/Retinol, ho\u1eb7c<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xen k\u1ebd ng\u00e0y: m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00f9ng treatment m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng \u2013 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi da y\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, n\u00ean gi\u1ea3m s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-bat-buoc-chong-nang-khi-dung-gsc-giga-white-serum-khong\"><\/span><b>C\u00f3 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng khi d\u00f9ng GSC Giga White Serum kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3. D\u00f9 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n serum kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 acid t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 (m\u1edd n\u00e1m, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tia UV k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t melanin tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng da s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 nguy c\u01a1 n\u00e1m quay l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t cao.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-giga-white-serum-co-dung-duoc-cho-phu-nu-mang-thai-khong\"><\/span><b>GSC Giga White Serum c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng khi d\u00f9ng cho ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai\/cho con b\u00fa \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9. Khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb chung:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xem k\u1ef9 b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n, tr\u00e1nh t\u1ef1 \u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 s\u1ea3n khoa ho\u1eb7c b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Giga White Serum ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n sau sinh ho\u1eb7c khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd cho d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GSC Giga White Serum &#8211; Tinh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng m\u1edd th\u00e2m c\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da \u00c1 \u0110\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":6298,"comment_status":"open","p